summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Lane Street from Thirtieth Avenue South to Thirty-fourth Avenue South et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 24346, creating Local Improvement District No. 2348 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
